&lt;li&gt;C-terminal domain of amino acid dehydrogenases (an extra N-terminal helix displaces the C-terminal helix [[cite:PUB00025375]]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NAD-binding domain of certain potassium channels [[cite:PUB00025981]]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;C-terminal domain of the transcriptional repressor Rex [[cite:PUB00032388]]&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ornithine cyclodeaminase [[cite:PUB00031693]]&lt;/li&gt;
